  calc
    edist («expr +ᵥ » (f x) (g x)) («expr +ᵥ » (f y) (g y)) ≤ edist (f x) (f y) + edist (g x) (g y) :=
      edist_vadd_vadd_le _ _ _ _
    _ ≤ Kf * edist x y + Kg * edist x y := add_le_add (hf x y) (hg x y)
    _ = (Kf + Kg) * edist x y := (add_mul _ _ _).symm
